column5: Was wondering if anyone might know of someone in the GTA or surrounding area that does repair's and maintenance on both spinning and baitcasting reels.  Thanks, M
aikman's in missisauga iuf you are on the west side.. there's someone on the east side too.  rocky's in orillia.
Feel free to PM me, i do baitcaster upgrade, maintenance, clean and lube, as well as repairs. My rates are much more competitive than aikmans.
